<div class="banner mb-3" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)), url(https://img.freepik.com/free-vector/mobile_53876-166870.jpg?semt=ais_hybrid);">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="banner-text-wrapper w-50">
      <h1 style="font-size: 60px; font-family: Alice; font-weight: lighter;">YOUR DREAMS</h1>
      <h1 style="font-size: 30px; font-weight: lighter;">Rent and explore captivating dreamscapes, all while you rest!</h1>
      <p> Your perfect night is just a dream away.</p>
      <p><i>â€” because why let your imagination sleep? ðŸŒ™âœ¨</i></p>
